title: Man Yanling
text: Man Yanling is a Chinese <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. She was part of the Chinese team at the <a href="1995%20FIFA%20Women%27s%20World%20Cup">1995 FIFA Women's World Cup</a> and <a href="1999%20FIFA%20Women%27s%20World%20Cup">1999 FIFA Women's World Cup</a>, where the team placed fourth and second, respectively.
